# Exchange Server On-Prem Deployment Log

## Overview
This repository documents my setup and configuration of Microsoft Exchange Server on-prem, referencing Ali Tajran's documentation.

## Environment
- Windows Server 2022
- Exchange Server 2019 CU13
- AD Domain: contoso.local
- Server Role: Mailbox Role

## Steps Completed
### 1. Prepare Active Directory
- Installed prerequisites
- Ran `Setup.exe /PrepareSchema`
- Ran `Setup.exe /PrepareAD`

### 2. Install Exchange Server
- Downloaded latest CU
- Installed UCMA
- Installed prerequisites using PowerShell (added commands)

### 3. Post-Installation Tasks
- Configured receive connectors
- Configured send connectors
- Imported SSL certificate
- Configured virtual directories

